    "validation_status": "Type 4 (Жилой дом) is the validated, floor-aware mapping used by scenario runs. The remaining types are best-effort starters keyed on physical_object_function; codes left null where a single VRI is ambiguous (these are not exercised by current scenario runs, which fetch one object type at a time).",
    "version": 1
  },

